

=Bio=

Interested in creating an information source, outreach movement and networking activity for local communities, especially my own, and to focus on food production as an initial step in this process. i have recently graduated from a Permaculture PCR course and am interested in introducing those principles as a main feature of a local food production movement. Also such a movement would be based on what the members of a given locality could accomplish in terms of peer to peer networking in order to build the informational resources and communication systems to accomplish such a task.

